    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007810/extras/200673d9a745e12bfe56d20366bac41c.avif?t=1694178435\" width=616 height=280 /></span><br>《重明鸟》是一款包含剧情、探索、解谜的游戏。探索无缝横版的世界，解开充满挑战性的谜题。你将在游戏中控制 “鹞”和 “玄”2位角色，他们踏上了危险的旅程，寻找传说中的重明鸟来化解阴霾。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007810/extras/b3614353af3136ff802e1b7c1cf3576e.avif?t=1694178435\" width=614 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有韵味的中国风</h2>我们将各种元素融入进了中国风！游戏内使用了大量的中国传统文物，并赋予了他们独特的形象、性格与功能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007810/extras/529bfc54bc6693ad9d64a8357b44b569.avif?t=1694178435\" width=616 height=260 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >穿越维度</h2>平面化游戏出现了纵深感？你没看错，虽然是平面化的游戏，在关卡和表现上做出了纵深感的玩法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007810/extras/ee93e93a7c4143f9397a2f8cf0e4e42a.avif?t=1694178435\" width=616 height=260 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >张弛有度的谜题体验</h2>我们以剧情、冒险和解谜相结合的方式来保证玩家的体验, 面对机关陷阱不会太频繁太累，也不会因过于密集的解谜点而感到过于烧脑。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007810/extras/09789a6bfc62ca98b8e180b9499256d2.avif?t=1694178435\" width=616 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不一样的收集玩法</h2>旅途中还会遇到上百个形色各异的角色。主角结识并帮助他们后，他们会加入队伍，并为主角提供“真气值”来触发以后的机关。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1007810/extras/e7eff29f83d042a866cc09efc55294f0.avif?t=1694178435\" width=616 height=208 /></span>",
